28
00:01:32,660 --> 00:01:34,600
雖然很積極 但同時也感到迷惘

29
00:01:34,600 --> 00:01:36,840
不要趁這時候 就這樣離開我喔

30
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:40,530
Oh yeah

31
00:01:40,950 --> 00:01:45,060
Do the dancing with you

32
00:01:45,370 --> 00:01:49,750
Do the dancing with who?

33
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:53,800
Do the dancing with you

